casebody.data:
Mickey AXELBAND, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
MARLINS STADIUM OPERATOR, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D18-0327 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. OCTOBER 5, 2018 ROTHENBERG, C.J., and SALTER and LINDSEY, JJ., concur.

Upon the Court's own motion, it is ordered that this appeal from the Circuit Court for Miami-Dade County, Florida is dismissed for failure to comply with this Court's order dated September 4, 2018, and with the Florida Rules of Appellate Procedure.
